dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents the county boundaries for Uganda. These are the Level 4 admininstrative boundaries (ADM4). This layer is based on 2006 data.These data are intended for researchers, students, policy makers and the general public for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production.
